(This, the first experiment on this platform, aims to test and model moral and strategic choices in) Tj
T* (the simplest possible social choices, called binary Dictator Games, where one person chooses) Tj
T* (how many payoffs to allocate between themselves and another participant.  Our goal is to) Tj
T* (predict future choices based on past choices, where choices are defined by payoffs.) Tj
